[This is a bit of good news in this horrible situation of Hendra
virus. This is also a nice summary of properties, horses, and people
being affected by testing and quarantines. Of course, those families
who are anxiously waiting for their loved ones to be cleared are not
counted here and are likely still tense about the situation. - Mod.TG]
